Fund (NTF). Single applicants are required to make a minimum non-refundable donation of $235,000 to the NTF.<\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-ea68e84 elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"ea68e84\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<h2 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">Real Estate Investment<\/h2>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-ffea86f elementor-invisible elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"ffea86f\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-settings=\"{&quot;_animation&quot;:&quot;xpro-anim-mask-from-left&quot;}\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p>Acquire Citizenship by investing $270,000 in a real estate project approved by the Government of Grenada. The Real Estate Investment is Refundable after holding it for minimum 5 years.\u00a0<\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-f17bd9a e-con-full e-flex e-con e-child\" data-id=\"f17bd9a\" data-element_type=\"container\" data-e-type=\"container\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-a36037d elementor-widget elementor-widget-image\" data-id=\"a36037d\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"image.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"800\" height=\"533\" src=\"https:\/\/forecastmigration.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/09\/daacb94022.jpg\" class=\"attachment-large size-large wp-image-8303\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https:\/\/forecastmigration.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/09\/daacb94022.jpg 1000w,